	.section.container.booking-terms-container
		.row
			.columns.twelve
				.booking-terms-wrapper
					.content-title
						span Booking Terms
						
					.content-calibre
						span Check-In and Check-Out
					ul.terms
						li Check-In – 14:00 ; Check-Out – 12:00.
						li Please note that early check-in / late check-out is subject to availability and cannot be confirmed in advance. However, you can leave your luggage with us while you’re out exploring Luang Prabang.
						
					.content-calibre
						span Price Policies
					ul.terms
						li High Season: 01 Oct 2017 – 20 Apr 2018.
						li Low Season: 21 Apr 2018 – 30 Sep 2018.
						li Sales Tax is included in the room rates. We do not have service charge, and tipping is at your discretion.
						li All prices are in US Dollars. Rates include daily breakfast, free Wi-Fi, in-room coffee and tea making facilities and complimentary use of hotel bicycles.
					
					.content-calibre
						span Child Policy
					ul.terms
						li Children aged five and below stay for free. Maximum occupancy for Frangipani Rooms (regardless of age): four people.
						li Children must be accompanied by their parents at all times.
					
					.content-calibre
						span Cancellation
					ul.terms
						li Cancellation of hotel reservations received less than 72 hours prior to your arrival will incur the full cost of the first night of the stay.
						li Cancellation of hotel reservations received less than 24 hours prior to your arrival or no-show will result in 100% of your room rate for your entire stay being charged to your credit card.

	
